column4: Hello. Any idea why the Google browser crashes when I go to the Google page?

Hello. I get this error from Google browser chromium when it crashes when I go to the Google page: [13:20:338584722:ERROR:platform_thread_posix.cc(251)] Not implemented reached in static void base::PlatformThread::SetThreadPriority(base::PlatformThreadHandle, base::ThreadPriority)
